                "venue": "",
                "citation_count": 14,
                "reference_count": 83,
                "abstract": "Instructional interventions are necessary in introductory college physics so that differences in preparation do not generate differences in outcomes for women, underrepresented ethnic or racial minorities, and first-generation college students.",
